title: "Project 1: Spam Mail Detector"
---

* Created a tool that detect spam mails becuase spam has been a major problem in day-to-day lifes of a customer.
* Naive Bayes classifier algorithm has been used on the context classification of each email, with a strong assumption that the words included in the email are independent of each other.
* Built a client facing API using Flask.

